{"tid":415063,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「集思廣益」有無人另一半棚牙極亂","createTime":"2017-09-26T16:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T01:23:38.000Z","uid":39153,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6410577149ff2696d20419a5775b5ccad08fb7be","tid":415063,"uid":39153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:24:41.000Z","msg":"背景交代<br />\n成家我一個棚牙唔齊，所以一到十六七歲就去箍，而我成家都好在意牙齒。<br />\n<br />\n日子耐左，屋企人有問起幾時可以見一見<br />\n<br />\n雖則佢棚牙唔齊係初頭一識就知，但屋企人肯定會好似之前對前度咁，係咁chur佢箍牙/chur我叫佢箍。<br />\n<br />\n而佢覺得自己棚牙唔好睇，兩個原因一直唔肯箍，一係怕痛，二係就三十年紀大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n已經拖左大半年，黎緊有中秋、聖誕、我生日、過年⋯⋯<br />\n如何是好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8dede7cbf1e5a05e4f5904d42a1f6364886a9a","tid":415063,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:27:15.000Z","msg":"成30歲人先箍牙邊頂得順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除時剝個牙都要休幾日"},{"pid":"744d90fe29311730ca7756b6fb5cc322804b8a63","tid":415063,"uid":62121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:50:03.000Z","msg":"其實無想像中咁痛<br />\n我18歲先箍牙 剝左4隻 少痛<br />\n上箍果日 牙醫叫我擘大個口.. 等左陣 我都唔知佢搞乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知過左幾個字  姑娘話「得啦 搞掂啦～」 我呆撚左 原來箍已上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一啲痛都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果位醫生手勢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e521137a8b3caccfaf686261399fcd36986cf8","tid":415063,"uid":6031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:04:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實無想像中咁痛<br />\n我18歲先箍牙 剝左4隻 少痛<br />\n上箍果日 牙醫叫我擘大個口.. 等左陣 我都唔知佢搞乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知過左幾個字  姑娘話「得啦 搞掂啦～」 我呆撚左 原來箍已上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一啲痛都無<img src=\"/assets/faces